    "en": {
      "title": "Jackson Anthony was admitted to Colombo National Hospital",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Veteran actor Mr. Jackson Anthony, who was injured in the accident where a cab in which he was traveling, collided with a wild elephant in Anuradhapura, Mr. Jackson Anthony has been admitted to the Colombo National Hospital for further treatment.",
        "The accident took place last night and three people who were traveling in the cab were injured in the accident. First they were admitted to Anuradhapura Hospital and then Mr. Jackson Anthony was admitted to Colombo National Hospital for further treatment.",
        "While returning from a shooting in Anuradhapura, the cab collided with an elephant and the elephant overturned the cab."
      ],
